{
  "stem": "10588.9",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I wouldn't ask what it is, because I figured, if she wants to give me, she will.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I didn't--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Malka Fuchs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have a photograph from her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because every banquet, they made a photograph.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have a photograph with Kalfus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what she gave me was the photograph we hired with my father when was seven years old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, I saw, you only have what you give away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that still is not the end of the story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we came here, we didn't have any relatives for many years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was so happy for anyone who had a family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember my late son Michael, when we lived in two houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Many apartments, but this was the second house I lived in America.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember when we moved into the first home, we saw an elderly lady, may she rest in peace, Rose Fitch.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, Lady, I don't have a grandmother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you please be my grandmother?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was a kind lady.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She lived to 96.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was his adopted grandmother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we didn't have a family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my children always ask me, how come we didn't have a family?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I have one conversation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I never thought that I'm going to be testifying on the Holocaust at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I saved it, and now it's a poem that everybody wants to hear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If you want, I'll share it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the reason that it affected our whole lives, because you can never replace the irreplaceable loss of a life, of a home, of a family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I know it's someplace.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was my conversation with my late son, Michael.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I need to find it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Is it about your grandmother?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is my conversation with Michael.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My grandmother have a poem too.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
